    "bio": "Pridevel | n8n Expert\n\nAutomations that save you hours, not just clicks.\nI’m Dipen, an n8n specialist helping founders, marketers, and teams automate workflows, scale operations, and eliminate repetitive tasks.\nHere you'll find ready-to-use n8n workflows, templates, and automation packs designed to plug straight into your stack and start delivering value from day one.",
